ce%20cameras%20in%20Kyiv%20to%20coordinate%20a%20huge%20missile%20attack%20on%20the%20city%2C%20Ukraine's%20security%20service%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Security%20Service%20of%20Ukraine%20(SBU)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FSBUkr%2F10757%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Telegram%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Russian%20intelligence%20had%20hacked%20two%20online%20surveillance%20cameras%20to%20spy%20on%20Ukraine's%20Defense%20Forces%20in%20the%20city%20and%20to%20prepare%20its%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SBU%20said%20it%20had%20since%20blocked%20the%20two%20cameras%2C%20which%20it%20said%20Russia%20used%20to%20spy%20on%20its%20air%20defense%20systems%20and%20check%20out%20where%20the%20city's%20critical%20infrastructure%20was%20located%20before%20it%20attacked%20Kyiv%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attacks%20on%20the%20city%20and%20its%20surroundings%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Frussia-ukraine-kharkiv-kyiv-2b23b1163c859a645b485d5c38035369%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekilled%20four%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20injured%20around%2070.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20fired%20almost%20100%20missiles%20at%20Kyiv%20and%20the%20eastern%20city%20of%20Kharkiv%2C%20Gen.%20Valerii%20Zaluzhnyi%2C%20the%20commander-in-chief%20of%20Ukraine's%20Armed%20Forces%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-seems-begin-ukraine-missile-barrage-it-saved-ammo-for-2023-12%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etargeting%20Ukraine's%20critical%20infrastructure%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20its%20energy%20systems%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20campaign%20that%20has%20escalated%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20hacked%20cameras%20involved%20in%20Tuesday's%20attack%20was%20on%20the%20balcony%20of%20an%20apartment%20building%20and%20was%20used%20by%20a%20nearby%20condo%20to%20monitor%20the%20local%20area.%20The