20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Held%20Up'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20elections%20for%20three%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seats%20from%20Delhi%20will%20take%20place%20on%20January%2019%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBeing%20National%20Convenor%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20I%20am%20held%20up%20in%20the%20process%20and%20run%20up%20to%20these%20critical%20elections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%2C%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Delhi%2C%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Balso%20quite%20occupied%20in%20planning%20and%20preparations%20for%20several%20programmes%20and%20functions%20for%20the%20Republic%20Day%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20such%20circumstances%2C%20I%20hope%20that%20you%20shall%20act%20as%20per%20law%20by%20transparently%20and%20fairly%20considering%20my%20objections%20as%20raised%20and%20indicated%20in%20my%20earlier%20responses%20dated%2002.11.2023%20and%2020.12.2023.%20In%20the%20meanwhile%2C%20I%20would%20be%20happy%20to%20respond%20to%20any%20questionnaire%20if%20you%20seek%20any%20information%2Fdocuments%2C%20which%20are%20in%20my%20knowledge%2Fpossession%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EObjections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20chief%20had%20not%20appeared%20before%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20when%20he%20was%20summoned%20on%20November%202%20and%20December%2021%20as%20well%2C%20and%20two%20other%20senior%20leaders%20of%20the%20party%20are%20in%20judicial%20custody%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%20Former%20Delhi%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%20was%20arrested%20in%20February%20last%20year%2C%20and%20AAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20first%20summons%20was%20issued%2C%20there%20has%20been%20intense%20speculation%20that%20the%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20would%20be%20arrested%20by%20the%20agency%20after%20his%20questioning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20claimed%20he%20knows%20of%20several%20cases%20where%20the%20agency%20had%20given%20a%20detailed%20explanation%20or%20response%20to%20queries%20by%20people%20issued%20summons%20under%20Section%2050%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%20but%20it%20had%20not%20even%20acknowledged%20the%20receipt%20of%20the%20submissions%20made%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20premier%20investigating%20agency%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20'non-disclosure%26quot%3B%20and%20'non-response'%20approach%20adopted%20by%20you%20cannot%20sustain%20the%20test%20of%20law%2C%20equity%20or%20justice.%20Your%20obstinacy%20tantamounts%20to%20assuming%20the%20role%20of%20judge%2C%20jury%20and%20executioner%20at%20the%20same%20time%20which%20is%20not%20acceptable%20in%20our%20country%20governed%20by%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BVested%20Interests%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20these%20circumstances%2C%20I%20therefore%2C%20once%20again%2C%20urge%20you%20to%20kindly%20respond%20to%20my%20earlier%20responses%20and%20clarify%20the%20position%20so%20as%20to%20enable%20me%20to%20understand%20the%20real%20intent%2C%20ambit%2C%20nature%2C%20sweep%20and%20scope%20of%20the%20purported%20inquiry%2Finvestigation%20for%20which%20I%20am%20being%20called%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AAP%20chief%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20alleged%20that%20while%20he%20was%20willing%20to%20cooperate%20and%20assist%20with%20any%20investigation%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20silence%20confirmed%20his%20apprehensions%20about%20%26quot%3Bcertain%20vested%20interests%20and%20extraneous%20as%20well%20as%20malafide%20considerations%20prevailing%20over%20any%20objective%2C%20rational%2C%20fair%20or%20impartial%20inquiry%20or%20investigations%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%20also%20questioned%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20summons%20and%20said%20that%20it%20had%20been%20sent%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20arresting%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20has%20the%20notice%20been%20sent%20right%20before%20elections%3F%20The%20notice%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20stop%20Kejriwal%20from%20campaigning%20in%20the%20(Lok%20Sabha)%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Lame%20Excuses'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20BJP%20called%20him%20the%20kingpin%20of%20the%20alleged%20scam.%20%26quot%3BOutright%20dishonest%20and%20sinister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20shaking%20in%20fear%20and%20making%20one%20after%20another%20lame%20excuse%20to%20skip%20ED%20summons%2C%26quot%3B%20news%20agency%20PTI%20quoted%20BJP%20national%20spokesperson%20Gaurav%20Bhatia%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20won't%20be%20wrong%20to%20say%20that%20(Arvind)%20Kejriwal%20is%20afraid%20today%20because%20he%20knows%20that%20his%20arrest%20is%20imminent%2C%20he%20is%20aware%20that%20he%20is%20the%20kingpin%20and%20has%20no%20answers.%20That's%20why%20he%20is%20trying%20to%20evade%20the%20process%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704286500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F3qlngjpo_arvind-kejriwal-1200_625x300_08_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-skips-ed-summons-busy-with-polls-happy-to-answer-questionnaire-arvind-kejriwal-on-summons-4793348%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20response%20to%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20on%20its%20summons%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20said%20he%20is%20busy%20with%20the%20Republic%20Day%20preparations%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20and%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bhappy%20to%20answer%26quot%3B%20any%20questionnai