A%22CHETHAN%20KUMAR%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nikesh%20Arora%2C%20Once%20Google's%20Highest%20Paid%20Executive%2C%20Is%20Now%20A%20Billionaire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENikesh%20Arora%20has%20repeatedly%20succeeded%20in%20winning%20big%20paychecks.%20At%20Google%2C%20he%20became%20the%20firm's%20highest-paid%20executive%20after%20getting%20a%20compensation%20package%20worth%20about%20%2451%20million%20in%202012%2C%20on%20his%20way%20to%20collecting%20stock%20awards%20worth%20at%20least%20%24200%20million%20by%20the%20time%20he%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoached%20in%202014%20by%20SoftBank%20Group%20Corp.'s%20Masayoshi%20Son%20%E2%80%94%20and%20touted%20as%20the%20legendary%20investor's%20likely%20successor%20%E2%80%94%20he%20amassed%20a%20%24135%20million%20first-year%20compensation%20package%20that%20broke%20Japanese%20records%20and%20made%20him%20the%20world's%20best-paid%20executive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20Nikesh%20Arora's%20latest%20stint%2C%20as%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20cybersecurity%20firm%20Palo%20Alto%20Networks%20Inc.%2C%20that's%20catapulted%20the%2055-year-old%20into%20the%20billionaire%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENikesh%20Arora%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalo%20Alto%20Networks%20handed%20Nikesh%20Arora%20a%20%24125%20million%20stock%20and%20options%20compensation%20package%20when%20he%20was%20hired%20in%202018.%20Thanks%20to%20a%20boom%20in%20cybersecurity%20software%20after%20a%20series%20of%20high-profile%20hacking%20incidents%20that%20disrupted%20casinos%2C%20ports%20and%20even%20Treasury%20markets%2C%20the%20company's%20share%20price%20has%20more%20than%20quadrupled%20since%20then%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Arora's%20stake%20is%20now%20worth%20%24830%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECombined%20with%20enormous%20pay%20awards%20he%20secured%20earlier%20in%20his%20career%2C%20Arora's%20net%20worth%20stands%20a