ski%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBarbara%20Corcoran%20said%20ageism%20is%20still%20a%20problem%20at%20work%20and%20over%2050s%20will%20struggle%20to%20land%20jobs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20older%20workers%20should%20try%20to%20appear%20young%20and%20energetic%20to%20boost%20their%20chances%20in%20interviews.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%202022%20AARP%20survey%20of%20over%2050s%20found%20that%2053%25%20were%20asked%20by%20employers%20to%20provide%20a%20birth%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAgeism%20is%20still%20alive%20and%20well%20in%20the%20workplace%20with%20older%20professionals%20often%20facing%20the%20short%20end%20of%20the%20stick%20in%20job%20interviews%2C%20but%20Shark%20Tank%20investor%20Barbara%20Corcoran%20offered%20some%20advice%20on%20how%20to%20beat%20the%20odds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E74-year-old%20Corcoran%2C%C2%A0%20founder%20of%20The%20Corcoran%20Group%2C%20was%20recently%20asked%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoUsYg_shsMc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elive%20Q%26amp%3BA%20on%20her%20Patreon%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20about%20how%20to%20turn%20ageism%20in%20the%20workplace%20into%20an%20asset.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorcoran%20first%20shared%20some%20sobering%20thoughts%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BAgeism%20is%20a%20problem%20and%20I'd%20be%20lying%20to%20you%20if%20I%20said%20'Don't%20worry%20about%20it.%20This%20is%20how%20you%20fix%20it%20up.'%20The%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20when%20you're%20applying%20for%20jobs%2C%20if%20you're%20over%2050%2C%20people%20are%20going%20to%20hesitate.%20They're%20going%20to%20see%20who%20else%20they%20have%20under%2050.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aarp.org%2Fresearch%2Ftopics%2Feconomics%2Finfo-2022%2Fworkforce-trends-older-adults-age-discrimination.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EA%202022%20AARP%20survey%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%202%2C945%20US%20adults%20aged%2050%20and%20over%20found%20that%2015%25%20of%20respondents%20who%20applied%20for%20a%20job%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years%20were%20rejected%20based%20on%20their%20age.%2053%25%20were%20asked%20by%20employers%20to%20provide%20a%20birth%20date%2C%20and%2047%25%20were%20asked%20to%20provide%20a%20graduation%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E93%25%20of%20respondents%20also%20said%20that%20discrimination%20against%20older%20workers%20is%20common%20in%20the%20workplace%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorcoran%20explained%20that%20over%2050s%20needed%20to%20create%20an%20impression%20of%20being%20young%20and%20energetic%20in%20an%20interview.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPut%20your%20best%20foot%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20Corcoran%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20go%20into%20that%20interview%20whether%20that%20be%20a%20Zoom%20interview%20or%20in%20person%2C%20you%20gotta%20look%20your%20best.%20Vitality%20is%20what%20fools%20an%20employer.%20If%20you%20walk%20in%20there%2C%20vital%2C%20full%20of%20life%2C%20and%20enthusiasm%20they're%20going%20to%20forget%20that%20you're%2053%20and%20think%20you're%20acting%20younger%20and%20be%20more%20attracted%20to%20you.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20noted%20that%20her%20older%20employees%20tended%20to%20have%20more%20experience%20and%20wisdom%20and%20that%20they%20should%20use%20that%20to%20their%20advantage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hire%20many%20people%20that%20are%20older%20and%20you%20know%20what%20I%20find%20better%20about%20older%20people%20very%20often%20is%20they%20have%20so%20much%20more%20wisdom.%20There's%20no%20circumstance%20that%20they%20run%20into%20that%20they%20haven't%20seen%20before%20and%20have%20a%20solution%20for.%20So%20you%20take%20a%20lot%20less%20training%2C%20be%20aware%20of%20that.%20You%20have%20a%20lot%20more%20life%20experience%20and%20judgment%20you%20bring%20forth.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-can-older-workers-prove-ageism-and-age-bias-in-hiring-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EOne%2056-year-old%20IT%20specialist%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Business%20Insider's%20Rebecca%20Knight%20in%202023%20that%20after%20being%20laid%20off%20he%20was%20rejected%20by%2031%20companies%20despite%20having%20worked%20at%20two%20big%20tech%20firms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERay%20Peeler%2C%20an%20associate%20legal%20counsel%20at%20the%20Equal%20Employment%20Opportunity%20Commission%20told%20Knight%20that%20it's%20difficult%20to%20prove%20age%20discrimination%20in%20interviews%20unless%20there's%20specific%20evidence%20to%20show%20that%20recruiters%20decided%20not%20to%20hire%20someone%20because%20of%20their%20age.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarbara-corcoran-said-older-workers-should-act-younger-in-interviews-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704284897000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6551f504385143459e8bd819%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarbara-corcoran-said-older-workers-should-act-younger-in-interviews-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Barbara%20Corcoran%20said%20workers%20over%2050%20should%20act%20energetic%20and%20enthusiastic%20in%20job%20interviews%3A%20%26quot%3BVitality%20is%20what%20fools%20an%20employer.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbhaimiya%40insider.com%20(Sawdah%20Bhaimiya)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarbara-corcoran-said-older-workers-should-act-younger-in-interviews-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Walt%20Disney%20Inks%20Deal%20With%20Investor%20ValueAct%20Amid%20Nelson%20Peltz%20Proxy%20Battle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704284853000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fu