A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-kevat%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Warner%20gets%20'Guard%20of%20Honour'%20from%20Pak%20players%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704283995000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106519305%2Cimgsize-83920.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fwatch-david-warner-gets-guard-of-honour-from-pakistan-players-in-his-farewell-test-in-sydney%2Farticleshow%2F106519311.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22David%20Warner%2C%20the%20left-handed%20batsman%2C%20has%20amassed%20a%20remarkable%20total%20of%208%2C695%20runs%20in%20111%20Test%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2044.58.%20This%20impressive%20record%20comprises%2026%20centuries.%20Notably%2C%20his%20highest%20individual%20score%20of%20an%20unbeaten%20335%20runs%20was%20achieved%20against%20Pakistan%20in%202019.%20Warner's%20consistent%20and%20prolific%20performances%20have%20solidified%20his%20position%20as%20a%20key%20contributor%20to%20Australian%20cricket%20over%20the%20course%20of%20his%20Test%20career.%20In%20the%20current%20Test%20series%20against%20Pakistan%2C%20Warner%20has%20demonstrated%20his%20batting%20prowess%20by%20accumulating%20208%20runs%20in%20the%20two%20matches%2C%20maintaining%20an%20impressive%20average%20of%2052.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fwatch-david-warner-gets-guard-of-honour-from-pakistan-players-in-his-farewell-test-in-sydney%2Farticleshow%2F106519311.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20A%201st%2C%20India%20To%20Launch%20Its%20Big%20Communications%20Satellite%20On%20SpaceX%20Rocket%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20space%20agency%20will%20rely%20on%20SpaceX%20to%20launch%20its%20next%20generation%20heavy%20communications%20satellite%20named%20GSAT-20.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20the%20Department%20of%20Space%20and%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organization%20(ISRO)%20will%20use%20the%20Falcon-9%20heavy%20lift%20launcher%20which%20may%20liftoff%20from%20Florida%20on%20a%20dedicated%20Indian%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20also%20exposes%20the%20weak%20underbelly%20of%20ISRO%20which%20still%20lacks%20a%20rocket%20which%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20lift%20big%20communication%20satellites.%20ISRO%20Chairman%20S%20Somanath%20says%20India%20had%20to%20go%20to%20SpaceX%20since%20'no%20other%20rocket%20was%20available%20in%20time.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commercial%20arm%20of%20ISRO%2C%20New%20Space%20India%20Limited%20has%20signed%20a%20contract%20with%20SpaceX%20for%20a%20possible%20liftoff%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20this%20year.%20The%20SpaceX%20deal%20also%20signifies%20a%20significant%20shift%20since%20till%20now%20India%20relied%20heavily%20on%20the%20France%20led%20Arianespace%20consortium%20to%20launch%20the%20heavy%20satellites.%20India's%20own%20rockets%20lack%20the%20capacity%20for%20launching%20very%20heavy%20satellites%20to%20the%20geostationary%20orbit%20beyond%204%20ton%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NSIL%2C%20GSAT-20%20offers%20Ka-Ka%20band%20high%20through%20put%20(HTS)%20capacity%20with%2032%20beams%20having%20Pan-India%20coverage%20including%20Andaman%20%26amp%3B%20Nicobar%2C%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20and%20Lakshadweep%20islands.%20NSIL%20is%20realizing%20GSAT-20%20satellite%20through%20ISRO.%C2%A0%20The%20satellite%20weighs%204700%20kg%2C%20offers%20HTS%20capacity%20of%20nearly%2048Gpbs.%20The%20satellite%20has%20been%20specifically%20designed%20to%20meet%20the%20demanding%20service%20needs%20of%20remote%2F%20unconnected%20regions.%20Dr%20Radhakrishnan%20Durairaj%2C%20CMD%2C%20NSIL%20says%20this%20is%20the%20second%20demand%20driven%20communication%20satellite%20mission%20being%20undertaken%20by%20NSIL%20after%20the%20GSAT-24%20mission%20whose%20full%20capacity%20was%20leased%20out%20to%20Tata%20Play.%20Durairaj%20says%20this%20new%20satellite%20deal%20only%20confirms%20that%20the%20reform%20process%20undertaken%20by%20the%20government%20is%20yielding%20results.%20NSIL%20has%20not%20revealed%20who%20has%20bought%20the%20capacity%20of%20the%20satellite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20France%20and%20Arianespace%20was%20indeed%20a%20trusted%20all%20weather%20partner%20all%20along%20and%20India%20launched%2023%20of%20its%20heavy%20duty%20communications%20satellites%20on%20this%20rocket%20owned%20by%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency.%20Durairaj%20says%20but%20for%20a%2021%20st%20century%20new%20age%20public%20sector%20undertaking%20looking%20at%20bottom%20lines%20%60if%20commercials%20and%20readiness%20make%20sense%20we%20go%20for%20it'.%20It%20must%20also%20be%20acknowledged%20that%20Arianespace%20retired%20its%20most%20trusted%20rocket%20Ariane-5%20and%20the%20replacement%20Ariane-6%20has%20been%20much%20delayed.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GSAT%2020%20satellite%20will%20now%20be%20renamed%20GSAT-N2%20and%20it%20will%20essentially%20provide%20broadband%20internet%20access%20to%20remote%20areas.%20This%20will%20obviously%20be%20in%20competition%20with%20OneWeb%20and%20Starlink%20who%20may%20get%20licenses%20soon%20since%20the%20new%20Telecom%20law%20paves%20way%20for%20them%20to%20launch%20their%20services.%20Other%20players%20actively%20wooing%20the%20space%20based%20internet%20service%20provider%20market%20is%20Reliance%20Jiospace.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20heaviest%20rocket%20dubbed%20the%20Bahuballi%20or%20the%20Launch%20Vehicle%20Mark%203%20can%20lift%20only%204000%20kilogram%20satellites%20to%20the%20geo-stationary%20orbit.%20Mr.%20S%20Somanath%20has%20been%20stressing%20the%20need%20to%20urgently%20build%20a%20heavier%20rocket%20called%20the%20Next%20Generation%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(NGLV)%20which%20can%20lift%20up%20to%2010%2C000%20kilograms%20to%20the%20same%20orbit%2C%20it%20is%20already%20being%20designed%20at%20the%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Center%20and%20will%20take%20few%20more%20years%20to%20become%20a%20reality.%20Somanath%20says%20%60India's%20launch%20capability%20has%20to%20be%20enhanced%20to%20meet%20future%20needs%2C%20while%20being%20cost%20competitive'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704283980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-11%2Fq9cms5ao_spacex-falcon-9-rocket-650_625x300_11_November_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-a-first-india-to-launch-its-satellite-on-spacexs-falcon-9-rocket-4792333%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20space%20agency%20will%20rely%20on%20SpaceX%20to%20launch%20its%20next%20generation%20heavy%20communications%20satellite%20named%20GSAT-20.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-a-first-india-to-launch-its-satellite-on-spacexs-falcon-9-rocket-4792333%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-a-first-india-to-launch-its-satellite-on-spacexs-falcon-9-rocket-4792333%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-a-first-india-to-launch-its-satellite-on-spacexs-falcon-9-rocket-4792333%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Most%20On-Time%20Airline%20In%202023%20Filed%20For%20Bankruptcy%20In%202020%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20New%20Year's%20resolution%20includes%20flying%20the%20most%20punctual%20airlines-in%20addition%20to%20choosing%20the%20best%20airports-%20the%202023%20annual%20on-time%20performance%20results%20from%20Cirium%2C%20published%20January%202%2C%20should%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aviation%20analytics%20company%20studies%20data%20on%20more%20than%2035%20million%20flights%20a%20year%2C%20including%20schedules%2C%20airline%20fleets%20and%20airports%2C%20to%20deliver%20insights%20on%20the%20aviation%20industry%20at%20large.%20For%20its%20annual%20airline%20on-time%20performance%20rankings%2C%20which%20it%20has%20been%20publishing%20for%20more%20than%2015%20years%2C%20Cirium%20examined%20600%20sources%20of%20flight%20data%20that%20spanned%20the%20entirety%20of%202023%20to%20determine%20whether%20airlines%20have%20met%20their%20published%20scheduled%20arrival%20times.%20Arriving%20within%2014%20minutes%20and%2059%20seconds%20of%20that%20scheduled%20arrival%20is%20considered%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20compensate%20for%20airlines'%20differing%20sizes%20and%20operating%20models%2C%20Cirium%20adds%20consideration%20for%20passenger%20carrying%20capacity%20and%20the%20number%20of%20regions%20the%20airline%20serves.%20To%20qualify%20for%20the%20global%20category%2C%20an%20airline%20must%20serve%20three%20or%20more%20international%20regions%20daily.%20All%20the%20data%20is%20crunched%20with%20the%20help%20of%20an%20advisory%20board%20made%20up%20of%20aviation%20industry%20experts%20to%20ensure%20accuracy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20most%20on-time%20global%20airline%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company's%20results%2C%20was%20Avianca.%20Based%20in%20Bogota%2C%20just%20under%2086%25%20of%20its%20flights%20arrived%20on%20time.%20That's%20a%20jump%20from%20sixth%20place%20in%20the%20rankings%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20airline%20that%20went%20through%20significant%20transformation-it%20rebranded%20itself%2C%20and%20it%20adopted%20a%20new%20business%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mike%20Malik%2C%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20at%20Cirium%20at%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20citing%20Avianca's%20rebound%20following%20a%20bankruptcy%20filing%20in%202020.%20The%20airline%20emerged%20out%20of%20Chapter%2011%20reorganization%20in%202021%2C%20slashing%20its%20debts%20and%20using%20a%20low-cost%20airline%20model%20with%20more%20affordable%20prices%20and%20point-to-point%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClosely%20following%20Avianca%20was%20Brazil-based%20Azul%20Brazilian%20Airlines%2C%20with%20an%2085.51%25%20on-time%20performance%2C%20and%20Qatar%20Airways%20at%2085.11%25.%20Delta%20Air%20Lines%20Inc.%20and%20Iberia%20rounded%20out%20the%20top%20five%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20the%20best%20airlines%20are%20not%20as%20punctual%20these%20days%20as%20they%20have%20been%20in%20the%20past.%20At%2085.73%25%2C%20this%20year's%20highest%20on-time%20arrival%20rate%20is%20%26quot%3Babout%202%20points%20lower%20than%20it%20used%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Malik.%20The%20highest%20in%202022%20was%2088.9%25%3B%20in%202019%2C%20it%20was%2086.7%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20notable%20is%20a%20dearth%20of%20Japanese%20airlines%2C%20which%20typically%20rank%20in%20the%20top%20players.%20Cirium%20indicated%20that%20it's%20unclear%20why%20the%20numbers%20from%20Japanese%20airlines%20dropped%20dramatically%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20North%20America%2C%20Delta%20was%20the%20most%20on%20time%20(84.7%25)%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22For%20North%20America%2C%20Delta%20was%20the%20most%20on%20time%20(84.7%25)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fjlq3t2ao_delta-airline-bloomberg_625x300_03_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20North%20America%2C%20Delta%20was%20the%20most%20on%20time%20(84.7%25)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20North%20America%2C%20Delta%20was%20the%20most%20on%20time%20(84.7%25)%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20for%20an%20airline%20that's%20ranked%20first%20regionally%20and%20among%20the%20top%20globally%20for%20three%20years%20in%20a%20row.%20Delta%20was%20followed%20by%20Alaska%20Airlines%20(82.25%25).%20But%20regional%20rankings%20reveal%20a%20few%20surprises%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20improvement%20in%20third%20place%2C%20American%20Airlines%20Group%20Inc.%20(80.61%25)%20brought%20its%20numbers%20up%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20Cirium%3A%20In%202022%2C%20American's%20punctuality%20rate%20came%20in%20at%2078.29%25.%20The%20airline%20also%20ranked%20third%20globally%20in%20Cirium's%20monthly%20on-time%20report%20for%20November%2C%20with%2086.5%25%20of%20its%20flights%20arriving%20on%20time%20during%20a%20busy%20Thanksgiving%20travel%20period.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfrican%20and%20Middle%20Eastern%20carriers%20also%20stood%20above%20Asia-Pacific%20airlines'%20on-time%20performance%20in%202023.%20It's%20a%20notable%20change%2C%20according%20to%20Cirium%2C%20which%20noted%20that%20this%20may%20be%20because%20those%20regions%20were%20able%20to%20provide%20capacity%20for%20the%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20second%20year%20in%20a%20row%2C%20Oman%20Air%20was%20the%20most%20punctual%20airline%20for%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20Africa.%20Its%2092.53%25%20on-time%20performance%20was%20followed%20by%20Safair%20and%20Royal%20Jordanian.%20In%20Asia-Pacific%2C%20Japan's%20All%20Nippon%20Airways%20was%20the%20most%20on-time%20at%20just%2082.75%25.%20Japan%20Airlines%20and%20India-based%20IndiGo%20rounded%20out%20the%20top%20three%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Europe%2C%20Madrid-based%20Iberia%20Express%20(84.5%25)%20topped%20the%20rankings%2C%20followed%20by%20Iberia%20and%20Norwegian%20Air%20Shuttle.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatin%20America's%20winner%20also%20had%20strong%20results%3A%20Copa%20Airlines%20had%20an%20annual%20on-time%20performance%20of%2089.46%25.%20(Copa%2C%20Oman%20Air%2C%20and%20Safair%20are%20among%20the%20airlines%20that%20did%20not%20qualify%20for%20the%20global%20rankings.)%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20low-cost%20carriers%2C%20South%20Africa-based%20Safair%20won%20the%20top%20spot%2C%20followed%20by%20Hong%20Kong%20Express%20and%20Azul%20Brazilian%20Airlines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%2