%20protest%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20veteran%20grapplers%20Bajrang%20Punia%2C%20Sakshi%20Malik%20and%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20putting%20all%20wrestling-related%20activities%20to%20a%20halt%20and%20ruining%20the%20future%20of%20children%20pursuing%20the%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20given%20years%20of%20my%20life%20to%20wrestling%20and%20retired%20recently%20so%20you%20can%20tell%20how%20stressed%20I%20am%20mentally.%20There%20is%20an%20IT%20cell%20of%20Brij%20Bhushan%20on%20social%20media.%20These%20protestors%20are%20his%20people%20and%20running%20propaganda%20for%20him.%20Brij%20Bhushan%20was%20making%20allegations%20against%20us%20earlier%20too%20during%20the%20protest%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sakshi%20to%20the%20media%20in%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESakshi%20went%20on%20to%20clarify%20that%20they%20did%20not%20have%20any%20problem%20with%20the%20newly%20elected%20federation%2C%20except%20for%20the%20president%20Sanjay%20Singh.%20She%20also%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20she%20welcomes%20the%20suspension%20of%20newly-elected%20federation%20by%20the%20Union%20Sports%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wrestler%20also%20accused%20Brij%20Bhushan%20of%20targeting%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20only%20had%20a%20problem%20with%20Sanjay%20Singh.%20We%20do%20not%20have%20any%20problem%20with%20the%20new%20federation%20body%20or%20the%20Ad-hoc%20committee.%20I%20request%20PM%20Modi%20ji%2C%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20ji%20to%20ensure%20that%20Sanjay%20Singh%20has%20no%20involvement%20in%20WFI.%20It%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20government%20to%20ensure%20our%20safety.%20Brij%20Bhushan%20(BJP%20leader%20%26amp%3B%20former%20WFI%20chief)%20is%20targeting%20my%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sakshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESakshi%20said%20that%20even%20though%20she%20is%20retiring%2C%20she%20wants%20the%20wrestlers%20who%20will%20play%20in%20her%2058%20kg%20category%20to%20secure%20a%20gold%20or%20silver%20in%20the%20Paris%202024%20Olympics%20and%20outdo%20her%20bronze%20medal%20in%20the%202016%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20request%20the%20ad-hoc%20committee%20to%20hold%20nationals%20and%20camps%20for%20U15%2C%20U17%2C%20U20%20categories.%20No%20youngster%20should%20face%20any%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESakshi%20said%20that%20it%20would%20be%20great%20for%20women%20wrestlers%20if%20women%20are%20given%20some%20responsibilities%20in%20the%20federation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20say%20that%20I%20will%20step%20into%20administration.%20But%20If%20there%20are%20some%20women%20in%20the%20federation%2C%20it%20would%20be%20good%20for%20women%20wrestlers%2C%20Women%20wrestlers%20will%20be%20able%20to%20go%20and%20express%20themselves%20freely%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ad%20hoc%20committee%20for%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20on%20Monday%20announced%20it%20would%20host%20the%20National%20Coaching%20Camp%20for%20Senior%20Wrestlers%20in%20preparation%20for%20the%20forthcoming%20Asian%20Olympics%20qualifying%20and%20World%20qualifying%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20this%2C%20the%20committee%20has%20scheduled%20the%20Senior%20National%20Championships%20for%20wrestling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20was%20announced%20following%20a%20press%20release%20by%20the%20ad%20hoc%20committee.%20The%20senior%20National%20Championships%20will%20take%20place%20from%20February%202%20to%205%20in%20Jaipur%20and%20will%20be%20orchestrated%20by%20the%20Railway%20Sports%20Promotion%20Board%20(RSPB).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tournament%20will%20include%20competitions%20across%20senior%20freestyle%2C%20Greco-Roman%2C%20and%20women's%20categories%2C%20providing%20a%20comprehensive%20platform%20for%20wrestlers%20to%20showcase%20their%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20Senior%20National%20Championships%2C%20the%20National%20Coaching%20Camp%20(NCC)%20will%20be%20conducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20men's%20camp%20(encompassing%20Greco-Roman%20and%20free%20style)%20will%20be%20held%20at%20SAI%20NRC%20Sonepat%2C%20while%20the%20women's%20camp%20will%20be%20held%20at%20SAI%20NSNIS%20Patiala.%20The%20NCC%20will%20select%20medalist%20wrestlers%20from%2030%20weight%20divisions%20across%20the%20senior%20freestyle%2C%20Greco-Roman%2C%20and%20women's%20categories%20of%20the%20Senior%20National%20Championships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coaching%20camp%20will%20begin%20on%20February%209%2C%202024%2C%20and%20extend%20until%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20in%202024.%20The%20primary%20focus%20of%20the%20NCC%20will%20be%20rigorous%20training%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Olympic%20qualifying%20tournaments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20qualifying%20tournaments%20include%20the%202024%20Asian%20Qualification%20Tournament%20set%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Bishkek%2C%20Kyrgyzstan%2C%20from%20April%2019-21%2C%20and%20the%202024%20World%20Qualification%20Tournament%20scheduled%20for%20Istanbul%2C%20Turkey%2C%20from%20May%209-12%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20NCC%20will%20prepare%20athletes%20for%20the%20Senior%20Asian%20Championships%2C%20which%20are%20slated%20to%20take%20place%20in%20Bishkek%2C%20Kyrgyzstan%2C%20from%20April%2011-16%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Sports%20Ministry%20had%20earlier%20suspended%20the%20sport's%20premier%20governing%20body%20in%20the%20country%20along%20with%20all%20its%20office-bearers%2C%20including%20the%20newly-elected%20president%20Sanjay%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20following%20its%20decision%2C%20the%20Ministry%20instructed%20the%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20(IOA)%20to%20form%20an%20ad%20hoc%20committee%20to%20manage%20and%20control%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704283080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ftuehpu2o_wrestlers-protest_625x300_03_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbrij-bhushans-propaganda-sakshi-malik-as-wrestlers-protest-against-her-vinesh-phogat-bajrang-punia-4793242%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20India%20wrestler%20and%20Olympic%20medalist%20Sakshi%20Malik%20on%20Wednesday%20accused%20the%20wrestlers%20protesting%20against%20her%20and%20other%20veteran%20wrestlers%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia%20of%20running%20propaganda%20against%20them%20for%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbrij-bhushans-propaganda-sakshi-malik-as-wrestlers-protest-against-her-vinesh-phogat-bajrang-punia-4793242%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbrij-bhushans-propaganda-sakshi-malik-as-wrestlers-protest-against-her-vinesh-phogat-bajrang-punia-4793242%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbrij-bhushans-propaganda-sakshi-malik-as-wrestlers-protest-against-her-vinesh-phogat-bajrang-punia-4793242%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hong%20Kong%20Box%20Office%20Struggled%20to%2025%25%20Gain%20in%202023%2C%20Remains%20%E2%80%98Deeply%20Unsatisfactory%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704282666000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2FGuilty-Conscience-1111_152581320163cadb432562e-1024x585-cr-res.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235860407%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hong%20Kong%20saw%20%E2%80%9CA%20Guilty%20Conscience%E2%80%9D%20become%20the%20highest-grossing%20film%20of%20all%20time%20at