com%2Fphoto%2F106518566.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fex-pakistan-pm-imran-khan-charged-with-contempt-of-electoral-watchdog-lawyer%2Farticleshow%2F106518566.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fex-pakistan-pm-imran-khan-charged-with-contempt-of-electoral-watchdog-lawyer%2Famp_articleshow%2F106518566.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fex-pakistan-pm-imran-khan-charged-with-contempt-of-electoral-watchdog-lawyer%2Famp_articleshow%2F106518566.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%3A%20Impact%20Of%20Supreme%20Court%20Backing%20SEBI%20Clean%20Chit%20To%20Adani%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20relief%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20today%20directed%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20to%20complete%20its%20investigations%20into%20the%20two%20(out%20of%2024)%20pending%20cases%20per%20law.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20said%20that%20independent%20reports%20or%20newspaper%20stories%20cannot%20be%20used%20to%20start%20a%20SEBI%20investigation.%20Questioning%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20George%20Soros-linked%20OCCRP%20report%20and%20Hindenburg%20report%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20that%20these%20cannot%20be%20independently%20verified%20and%20so%20can't%20be%20treated%20as%20dependable%20evidence.%20The%20court%20warned%20petitioners%20against%20filing%20pleas%20without%20adequate%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20decision%20is%20counter%20to%20a%20flurry%20of%20allegations%20against%20the%20Adani%20group%20since%20January%20last%20year%2C%20which%20negatively%20impacted%20the%20market%20cap%20of%20the%20conglomerate%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20bloodbath%20in%20India's%20stock%20market%20a%20year%20ago.%20The%20judgment%20made%20crystal%20clear%20that%20OCCRP%20cannot%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20doubting%20the%20capital%20markets%20regulator%20SEBI's%20investigation%20into%20the%20Hindenburg%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20found%20no%20merit%20in%20allegations%20of%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest%20against%20members%20of%20the%20court-appointed%20panel%2C%20as%20highlighted%20by%20the%20petitioner.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20delivered%20the%20verdict%20on%20a%20batch%20of%20petitions%20seeking%20a%20probe%20into%20allegations%20of%20stock%20manipulation%20and%20other%20irregularities%20against%20the%20Adani%20group%20made%20by%20US-based%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20the%20judgment%20was%20seen%20on%20the%20Indian%20stock%20market%2C%20with%20Adani%20stocks%20rallying%20up%20to%2010%20per%20cent%20and%20the%20conglomerate's%20market%20capitalisation%20crossing%20the%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20crore%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Hindenburg%20report%20had%20halted%20further%20capital%20raise%20of%20Adani%20group%20and%20crashed%20its%20stocks%20by%20about%20USD%20120%20billion.%20It%20impacted%20the%20pace%20at%20which%20India%20was%20rolling%20out%20energy%20and%20logistics%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20country%20as%20well%20as%20globally.%20It%20is%20now%20clear%20from%20the%20SEBI%20investigations%20that%20there%20was%20no%20basis%20for%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%2C%20and%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20concocted.%20However%2C%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20Indian%20economy%20and%20jobs%20has%20been%20significant%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Jaijit%20Bhattacharya%2C%20President%2C%20Centre%20for%20Digital%20Economy%20Policy%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20judgment%20reinforces%20the%20power%20and%20importance%20of%20regulatory%20bodies%20like%20SEBI%2C%20whose%20impartiality%20and%20legal%20stand%20was%20questioned%20by%20opposition%20parties%20and%20the%20government's%20critics.%20By%20not%20intervening%20in%20the%20investigation%20by%20SEBI%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20independence%20and%20respect%20for%20autonomous%20statutory%20regulatory%20bodies%20like%20SEBI.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20the%20bench%20didn't%20find%20any%20deliberate%20or%20intentional%20violation%20of%20the%20rules%20and%20regulations%20by%20SEBI%20to%20help%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20ordered%20SEBI%20to%20complete%20the%20pending%20investigations%20in%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20upheld%20the%20foreign%20portfolio%20investors%20(FPI)%20regulations%20alleged%20to%20have%20been%20used%20by%20the%20Adani%20group%20to%20inflate%20its%20stock%20prices.%20Dismissing%20calls%20of%20petitioners%20for%20SEBI%20to%20revoke%20amendments%20in%20FPI%20and%20LODR%20(Listing%20Obligations%20and%20Disclosure%20Requirements)%20regulations%2C%20the%20court%20said%20that%20these%20regulations%20were%20free%20from%20any%20flaws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20judgment%20maintains%20the%20exclusive%20domain%20of%20specialised%20regulators%20like%20SEBI.%20It%20is%20a%20settled%20legal%20proposition%20that%20judicial%20review%20is%20of%20the%20decision-making%20process%20and%20not%20an%20appeal%20against%20the%20decision.%20Once%20a%20constitutional%20court%20is%20satisfied%20with%20the%20decision-making%20process%2C%20there%20is%20no%20room%20for%20the%20court%20to%20supplant%20the%20actions%20of%20any%20specialised%20regulators%20with%20its%20own%20view%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Manish%20Mohan%2C%20advocate%2C%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20has%20instructed%20the%20government%20and%20SEBI%20to%20scrutinise%20legal%20violations%20by%20the%20short%20seller%20and%20to%20take%20appropriate%20action%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law.%20The%20court%20has%20also%20advised%20that%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20expert%20committee%20(which%20the%20court%20had%20appointed)%20to%20strengthen%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20Indian%20investors%20be%20taken%20into%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20appears%20that%20foreign%20players%20unleashed%20a%20pincer%20movement%20between%20Hindenburg%20report%20and%20OCCRP.%20One%20needs%20to%20question%20why%20the%20George%20Soros-backed%20organisation%20had%20a%20sudden%20interest%20in%20the%20capital%20markets%20of%20India%20and%20their%20functioning%3F%20We%20need%20to%20evolve%20institutional%20structures%20that%20are%20able%20to%20respond%20more%20rapidly%20to%20such%20threats%20and%20hit%20jobs%20so%20that%20our%20economy%20stays%20protected%2C%26quot%3B%20adds%20Mr%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoss%20of%20reputation%20can%20be%20damaging%20for%20a%20company.%20It%20takes%20years%20to%20salvage%20lost%20pride%20and%20opportunities.%20In%20the%20corporate%20law%20parlance%2C%20%26quot%3Bgoodwill%26quot%3B%20is%20considered%20an%20intangible%20asset.%20For%20a%20company%2C%20if%20the%20goodwill%20is%20dented%2C%20it%20is%20a%20huge%20setback%20considering%20reputational%20damage%2C%20downgraded%20credit%20ratings%20leading%20to%20higher%20cost%20of%20capital%2C%20and%20the%20flight%20of%20talent%20or%20difficulty%20in%20attracting%20external%20talent.%20The%20impact%20cannot%20be%20quantified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20judgment%20has%20reinforced%20the%20resilience%20of%20India's%20governance%20framework%2C%20the%20efficacy%20and%20impartiality%20of%20the%20country's%20market%20regulators%20and%20government%20departments%20which%20are%20responsible%20for%20safeguarding%20shareholders'%20interests%20and%20above%20all%20a%20judicial%20system%20which%20has%20followed%20the%20due%20process%20of%20law.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704282420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fbhp1gurg_adani-group_625x300_19_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fimpact-of-supreme-court-backing-sebi-clean-chit-to-adani-4793168%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20major%20relief%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20today%20directed%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20to%20complete%20its%20investigations%20into%20the%20two%20(out%20of%2024)%20pending%20cases%20per%20law.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fimpact-of-supreme-court-backing-sebi-clean-chit-to-adani-4793168%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22GST%20dept%20issues%20demands%2C%20penalties%20totaling%20over%20Rs%2019%20cr%20to%20Ceat%20Tyres%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704282301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F22%2Ffull%2F1697953296-4895.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgst-dept-issues-demands-penalties-totaling-over-rs-19-cr-to-ceat-tyres-124010300720_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20matters%20are%20being%20pursued%20against%20the%20orders%2C%20CEAT%20said%20the%20final%20impact%20on%20its%20financial%2C%20operation%20or%20other%20activities%20may%20not%20be%20ascertainable%20as%20of%20now%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgst-dept-issues-demands-penalties-totaling-over-rs-19-cr-to-ceat-tyres-124010300720_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard