bout%2010%25%20off%20the%20regular%20retail%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20eligible%2C%20you%20need%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20following%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20employee%20of%20any%20public%20or%20private%20K-12%20institution%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EK-12%20homeschool%20teachers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ECurrently%20serving%20school%20board%20members%2C%20as%20well%20as%20current%20PTA%20and%20PTO%20executives%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EFaculty%20or%20staff%20of%20any%20higher%20education%20institution%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EStudents%20attending%20(or%20accepted%20into)%20any%20higher%20education%20institution%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EParents%20making%20purchases%20on%20behalf%20of%20students%20at%20higher%20education%20institutions%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20rules%20are%20for%20US%20educators%20and%20students%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20slightly%20different%20education%20discount%20rules%20in%20other%20locales%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20the%20discount%2C%20visit%20Apple's%20Education%20Store%20and%20choose%20the%20product%20you%20want%20to%20buy%2C%20then%20check%20out%20in%20the%20normal%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20may%20ask%20you%20to%20confirm%20that%20you%20qualify%20as%20a%20student%20or%20educator%20at%20checkout.%20Students%20can%20generally%20provide%20a%20current%20photo%20ID%20from%20the%20school%20they%20are%20attending%2C%20a%20transcript%2C%20or%20report%20card.%20Educators%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20can%20submit%20a%20pay%20stub%20from%20an%20educational%20institution%20or%20a%20letter%20on%20the%20school's%20official%20letterhead%20verifying%20their%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHomeschool%20teachers%20qualify%20as%20well.%20They%20can%20provide%20a%20photo%20ID%20along%20with%20a%20letter%20of%20intent%20to%20homeschool%20addressed%20to%20their%20local%20school%20district%2C%20a%20Home%20School%20Legal%20Defense%20Association%20membe