80%9Csecond%20chance%20at%20life%E2%80%9D.%20Admitting%20that%20his%20revival%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnothing%20short%20of%20a%20miracle%E2%80%9D%2C%20Shreyas%20shared%20that%20he%20did%20not%20see%20this%20health%20setback%20coming.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20never%20hospitalised%20before%20in%20my%20life%2C%20not%20even%20for%20a%20fracture%20so%20I%20didn't%20see%20this%20coming.%20Don't%20take%20your%20health%20for%20granted.%20%3Cem%3EJaan%20hai%20toh%20Jahaan%20hai.%20%3C%2Fem%3EAn%20experience%20like%20this%20changes%20your%20perspective%20towards%20life.%20I%20started%20doing%20theatre%20at%2016%2C%20became%20a%20professional%20actor%20at%2020.%20For%20the%20past%2028%20years%2C%20I%20have%20just%20been%20focussing%20on%20my%20career.%20We%20take%20our%20families%20for%20granted.%20We%20think%20we%20have%20time.%20As%20a%20nation%2C%20we%20are%20not%20high%20on%20preventive%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanking%20his%20wife%20Deepti%2C%20the%20doctors%20and%20his%20well-wishers%20for%20their%20care%20and%20support%2C%20Shreyas%20Talpade%20offered%20details%20on%20his%20health%20condition.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20past%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20I%20have%20been%20working%20nonstop%20and%20travelling%20extensively%20for%20my%20films%2C%20%3Cem%3EPushpa%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5BShreyas%20dubbed%20for%20Allu%20Arjun%20in%20Hindi%5D%20or%20shows.%20However%2C%20for%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20I%20was%20feeling%20extremely%20fatigued.%20It%20was%20slightly%20unusual%20but%20since%20I%20was%20working%20nonstop%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20just%20a%20little%20exhausted%20which%20is%20normal.%20I%20loved%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20so%20I%20kept%20going.%20Of%20course%2C%20I%20got%20myself%20checked.%20I%20got%20an%20ECG%2C%202D%20Echo%2C%20sonography%20and%20blood%20tests%20done.%20My%20cholesterol%20was%20high%2C%20and%20I%20was%20taking%20medication%20for%20that.%20I've%20had%20a%20family%20history%20of%20heart%20ailments%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20was%20taking%20precautions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20what%20happened%20on%20the%20fateful%20day%2C%20Shreyas%20Talpade%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20shooting%20in%20Mumbai%20at%20the%20SRPF%20grounds%20close%20to%20Jogeshwari%20for%20Ahmed%20Khan's%20Welcome%20To%20The%20Jungle.%20We%20were%20doing%20army%20training%20sequences%20like%20swinging%20on%20a%20rope%2C%20falling%20into%20the%20water%20and%20everything%20was%20going%20smoothly%E2%80%A6Suddenly%2C%20after%20the%20last%20shot%2C%20I%20felt%20breathless%2C%20and%20my%20left%20hand%20started%20paining.%20I%20could%20barely%20walk%20to%20my%20vanity%20van%20and%20change%20my%20clothes.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20muscle%20pull%20since%20we%20were%20shooting%20action%20sequences.%20You%20don't%20think%20of%20the%20worst-case%20scenario%2C%20right%3F%20I%20had%20never%20experienced%20this%20kind%20of%20fatigue.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20further%2C%20the%3Cem%3E%20Iqbal%3C%2Fem%3E%20actor%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20soon%20as%20I%20got%20into%20the%20car%2C%20I%20felt%20I%20should%20head%20straight%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20but%20thought%20I%20should%20go%20home%20first.%20My%20wife%2C%20Deepti%2C%20saw%20me%20in%20that%20state%20and%20within%2010%20minutes%2C%20we%20were%20on%20our%20way%20to%20the%20hospital%20%5BAndheri's%20Bellevue%5D.%20We%20were%20almost%20there%20and%20could%20see%20the%20hospital%20gate%2C%20but%20the%20entry%20was%20barricaded%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20take%20a%20U-turn.%20The%20very%20next%20moment%20my%20face%20went%20numb%2C%20and%20I%20passed%20out.%20That%20was%20a%20cardiac%20arrest.%20My%20heart%20had%20stopped%20beating%20for%20those%20few%20minutes.%20Deepti%20couldn't%20get%20out%20of%20the%20car%20from%20her%20side%20of%20the%20door%20as%20we%20were%20stuck%20in%20traffic%2C%20so%20she%20climbed%20over%20me%20and%20got%20to%20the%20other%20side%20to%20call%20for%20help.%20A%20few%20people%20came%20to%20our%20rescue%20and%20rushed%20me%20inside.%20The%20doctors%20did%20CPR%2C%20electrical%20shock%2C%20that's%20how%20they%20revived%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShreyas%20Talpade%20revealed%20that%20two%20main%20arteries%20were%20blocked%20(one%20100%25%20and%20the%20other%2099%25)%20and%20that%20he%20had%20a%20stent%20placed%20through%20angioplasty.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20I%20regained%20my%20senses%2C%20the%20doctors%20told%20me%20that%20I%20smiled%20at%20them%20and%20conveyed%20sorry%20to%20my%20wife%20for%20putting%20her%20through%20this%20ordeal.%20I%20was%20kept%20under%20observation%20for%20five%20days.%E2%80%9D%20About%20his%20plans%20next%2C%20he%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20I%20am%20taking%20one%20day%20at%20a%20time%20and%20resting%20it%20out.%20The%20doctors%20said%20post%20six%20weeks%20I%20can%20get%20back%20to%20work.%20My%20producers%20told%20me%20to%20take%20it%20easy%2C%20too.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20relax%20now%2C%20be%20with%20family%20for%20now%2C%20spend%20time%20with%20my%20daughter%2C%20watch%20some%20films%20and%20read%20books.%20When%20something%20like%20this%20happens%2C%20your%20family%20suffers%20the%20most%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShreyas%20also%20admitted%20that%20he%20is%20immensely%20grateful%20to%20get%20a%20%E2%80%9Csecond%20chance%20at%20life%E2%80%9D.%20Explaining%20what%20he%20was%20taken%20back%20from%20the%20experience%2C%20the%20actor%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CClinically%2C%20I%20was%20dead.%20It%20was%20a%20massive%20cardiac%20arrest.%20A%20wake-up%20call%20would%20be%20an%20understatement.%20This%20is%20my%20second%20chance%20at%20life!%20I%20cannot%20tell%20you%20how%20thankful%20I%20am%20to%20everyone%20who%20played%20a%20role%20in%20saving%20my%20life.%20And%2C%20of%20course%2C%20my%20superwoman%20wife%2C%20who%20did%20everything%20she%20could%20in%20her%20capacity%20to%20save%20me.%20She%20is%20the%20reason%20we%20are%20talking%20today.%20It%20was%20overwhelming%20to%20receive%20this%20sort%20of%20love%20and%20care.%20These%20people%20gave%20me%20a%20second%20life%20and%20it's%20a%20debt%20I%20can%20never%20repay%2C%20Ahmed%20Khan%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Akki%20%5BAkshay%20Kumar%5D%20bhai%2C%20my%20friends%20and%20family%20have%20been%20visiting%20me%20at%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20when%20Shreyas%20Talpade%20returned%20home%20safely%2C%20the%20actor's%20wife%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshreyas-talpades-wife-deepti-writes-gratitude-note-my-life-is-back-home-4715450%5C%22%3E%20Deepti%20shared%20a%20gratitude%20note%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20life%2C%20Shreyas%2C%20is%20back%20home...%20safe%20and%20sound.%20I%20would%20argue%20with%20Shreyas%20saying%20I%20don't%20know%20where%20to%20put%20my%20faith%20in.%C2%A0%20Today%20I%20know%20the%20answer%20to%20my%20question%2C%20God%20almighty.%20He%20was%20with%20me%20that%20evening%20when%20this%20drastic%20event%20happened%20in%20our%20lives.%20I%20don't%20think%20I'll%20ever%20question%20his%20existence%20henceforth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanking%20the%20Good%20Samaritans%20who%20helped%20Deepti%20during%20the%20couple's%20hour%20of%20need%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wish%20to%20take%20a%20moment%20and%20thank%20the%20Good%20Samaritans%20of%20our%20city.%20That%20evening%20I%20called%20for%20help%2C%20sought%20a%20hand%20and%20I%20got%2010%20of%20them.%20While%20Shreyas%20lay%20inside%20the%20car%2C%20they%20didn't%20know%20who%20they%20were%20helping....yet%20they%20came%20running.%20To%20all%20those%20people%2C%20you%20were%20God%20incarnate%20that%20evening%20for%20us.%20Thank%20you.%20I%20hope%20my%20message%20reaches%20you.%20Please%20know%20that%20I%20shall%20be%20eternally%20grateful%20to%20you%20from%20the%20core%20of%20my%20being.%20That's%20the%20spirit%20of%20this%20great%20city%20Mumbai.%20That's%20what%20makes%20Mumbai.%20We%20were%20not%20left%20to%20fend%20for%20ourselves.%20We%20were%20taken%20