hoto%2Fmsid-106516548%2Cimgsize-11180.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fiphone-16-and-3-other-reasons-barclays-gave-for-downgrading-apple%2Farticleshow%2F106516528.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Barclays%20downgraded%20Apple%20stock%2C%20causing%20a%203.6%25%20drop%20to%20a%20seven-week%20low.%20The%20company%20now%20has%20its%20most%20bearish%20recommendations%20in%20two%20years.%20Barclays%20analysts%20expect%20weakness%20in%20iPhone%20volumes%20and%20mix%2C%20as%20well%20as%20little%20growth%20in%20Macs%2C%20iPads%2C%20and%20wearables.%20Apple's%20demand%20slowdown%20and%20performance%20in%20China%20are%20concerns.%20Barclays%20slightly%20lowered%20its%20price%20target%20for%20Apple%20stock.%20The%20note%20highlights%20continued%20iPhone%20weakness%2C%20stagnant%20growth%20in%20Mac%20and%20iPad%20segments%2C%20deceleration%20in%20Services%2C%20and%20diminishing%20returns%20on%20the%20Apple%20ecosystem.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BA%20Makes%20Allegation%20Against%20B%26quot%3B%3A%20Lawyer%20Explains%20Hindenburg%20Verdict%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESupreme%20Court%20lawyer%20Nalin%20Kohli%20has%20welcomed%20the%20top%20court's%20verdict%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20case%20today%20and%20slammed%20those%20who%20had%20demanded%20shifting%20of%20the%20probe%20from%20the%20capital%20markets%20regulator%20SEBI%20to%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20huge%20victory%20for%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20the%20report%20by%20the%20OCCRP%20-%20an%20organisation%20funded%20by%20billionaire%20George%20Soros%2C%20among%20others%20-%20can't%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20doubting%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board's%20(SEBI)%20investigation%20into%20the%20Hindenburg%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20larger%20question%20here%20is%2C%20a%20set%20of%20people%20for%20whatever%20be%20their%20motivations%2C%20decide%20to%20invoke%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20giving%20a%20complete%20go-by%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20SEBI%2C%20which%20is%20a%20statutory%20body...%20They%20say%20remove%20it%20(investigation)%20and%20give%20it%20to%20a%20third-party%2C%20or%20so-called%20independent%20investigation.%20SEBI%20is%20independent%3B%20it's%20not%20owned%20by%20a%20private%20entity%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kohli%20told%20NDTV%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20what's%20the%20basis%20for%20this%3F%20A%20report%20by%20a%20third%20party%20sitting%20in%20America%2C%20who%20may%20well%20be%20following%20an%20agenda%20to%20destabilise%20India's%20markets%20or%20do%20something%20like%20that%2C%20or%20gain%20in%20some%20manner%20from%20these%20kinds%20of%20sudden%20reports.%20So%20I%20think%20that's%20the%20big%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kohli%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20Senior%20Additional%20Advocate%20General%20of%20Assam%20and%20a%20BJP%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-hindenburg-case-supreme-court-backs-sebi-probe-4791214%5C%22%3EDelivering%20the%20judgment%20today%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20and%20justices%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20said%20there%20were%20no%20grounds%20to%20transfer%20the%20probe%20to%20an%20SIT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI%20has%20investigated%2022%20out%20of%20the%2024%20cases%20linked%20to%20the%20US-based%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research's%20allegations.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20gave%20the%20SEBI%20three%20months%20to%20complete%20investigation%20in%20the%20remaining%20two%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecond%2C%20what%20did%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20say%3F%20That%20SEBI%20will%20complete%20the%20probe.%20Obviously%2C%20the%20small%20investors%20have%20to%20be%20protected.%20If%20there%20is%20anything%20wrong%2C%20that's%20why%20the%20statutory%20agencies%20come%20in%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20this%20whole%20mechanism%20is%20in%20place.%20So%20I%20think%20running%20an%20agenda%20and%20using%20the%20courts%20for%20running%20that%20agenda%20is%20condemnable%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20rejected%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kohli%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20it%20might%20be%20reported%20by%20some%20people%20that%20a%20part%20of%20the%20order%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seemed%20to%20suggest%20that%20third-party%20information%20is%20not%20important%2C%20though%20that's%20exactly%20what%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20not%20said%2C%20Mr%20Kohli%20explained%3A%20%26quot%3BSo%20let%20me%20break%20it%20down%20in%20a%20simple%20sense.%20Assume%20'A'%20makes%20an%20allegation%20against%20'B'%2C%20whoever%20'A'%20is%2C%20whoever%20'B'%20is.%20'A'%20could%20have%20made%20the%20allegation%20under%20different%20circumstances%20-%20completely%20false%20allegations%20based%20on%20untruths%2C%20an%20allegation%20perhaps%20based%20on%20a%20suspicion%2C%20and%20an%20allegation%20based%20on%20information%20that%20is%20correct%20and%20truthful.%20All%20three%20possibilities%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20if%20it%20is%20based%20on%20the%20truth%20and%20correct%20information%2C%20that%20allegation%20that%20'A'%20makes%20against%20'B'%20can%20be%20investigated%2C%20say%20in%20this%20case%20the%20police%20and%20the%20police%20finds%20it%20correct.%20Now%2C%20there%20are%20two%20other%20circumstances%20-%20one%20is%20based%20on%20falsehood%2C%20and%20one%20is%20based%20on%20some%20suspicion.%20They%20will%20not%20cross%20the%20same%20threshold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20what%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20says%2C%20you%20can't%20blindly%20rely.%20And%20you%20certainly%20cannot%20be%20expected%20to%20blindly%20rely%20on%20something%20just%20because%20it's%20published%20abroad%2C%20which%20I%20would%20call%2C%20going%20one%20step%20further%2C%20colonial%20mindset.%20That%20there%20are%20set%20of%20people%20who%2C%20the%20minute%20it%20comes%20from%20across%20the%20borders%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20from%20Europe%20or%20America%2C%20they%20take%20as%20the%20gospel%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhereas%20the%20same%20people%20will%20even%20run%20down%20the%20honourable%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20its%20judgment%20if%20it%20doesn't%20suit%20them.%20That's%20an%20agenda.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitions%20on%20the%20Hindnburg%20issue%20were%20filed%20by%20lawyers%20Vishal%20Tiwari%20and%20ML%20Sharma%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Jaya%20Thakur%20and%20activist%20Anamika%20Jaiswal.%20The%20petitions%20had%20claimed%20the%20Adani%20Group%20inflated%20its%20share%20prices%2C%20and%20that%20the%20shares%20of%20some%20group%20entities%20had%20fallen%20sharply%20after%20the%20report%20by%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%20on%20January%2024%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20had%20termed%20the%20report%20a%20%26quot%3Bmalicious%20combination%20of%20selective%20misinformation%20and%20concealed%20facts%20relating%20to%20baseless%20and%20discredited%20allegations%20to%20drive%20an%20ulterior%20motive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704279480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fgc88c9f8_nalin-kohli_625x300_03_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-makes-allegation-against-b-supreme-court-lawyer-explains-hindenburg-verdict-to-ndtv-4792761%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%20Nalin%20Kohli%20has%20welcomed%20the%20top%20court's%20verdict%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20case%20today%20and%20slammed%20those%20who%20had%20demanded%20shif