-for-query%20allegations%20linked%20to%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20did%20not%20dismiss%20Ms%20Moitra's%20challenge%20against%20her%20expulsion%20from%20parliament%2C%20the%20court%20said%20it%20will%20first%20determine%20whether%20it%20has%20jurisdiction%20to%20hear%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Secretary%20General%2C%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20should%20not%20interfere%20in%20decisions%20taken%20inside%20parliament%2C%C2%A0since%20parliament%20has%20its%20own%20sovereignty%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20three%20organs%20under%20the%20Constitution%2C%20and%20parliament%20can%20internally%20manage%20disciplinary%20issues%20of%20its%20members%20through%20its%20in-house%20procedure%20which%20is%20not%20amenable%20to%20judicial%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20have%20the%20power%20of%20judicial%20review%2C%20we%20will%20investigate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20will%20also%20get%20three%20weeks%20to%20reply.%20The%20hearing%20will%20begin%20from%20March%2011%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20moment%2C%20Ms%20Moitra%20remains%20expelled%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20can't%20participate%20in%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20for%20now%20it%20won't%20comment%20on%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20issues%20raised%20by%20Ms%20Moitra%20in%20the%20challenge%20to%20her%20expulsion%2C%20but%20has%20kept%20the%20case%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20you%20admit%20that%20you%20shared%20OTP%20with%20Hiranandani%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20in%20the%20hearing%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20MPs%20do%20this%20with%20their%20secretaries%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20lawyer%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20appearing%20for%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20declined%20Ms%20Moitra's%20request%20for%20an%20early%20hearing%20citing%20the%20Budget%20session%2C%20due%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%2C%2049%2C%20was%20accused%20of%20taking%20bribes%2C%20including%20Rs%202%20crore%20in%20cash%20and%20%26quot%3Bluxury%20gift%20items%26quot%3B%2C%20from%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20in%20exchange%20for%20asking%20questions%20critical%20of%20the%20government%20in%20parliament.%20She%20was%20also%20accused%20of%20surrendering%20log-in%20credentials%20to%20a%20confidential%20account%20on%20the%20parliamentary%20website%2C%20so%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20could%20post%20those%20questions%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20denied%20the%20bribery%20charges%20but%20admitted%20to%20sharing%20the%20login%20details.%20She%20argued%20that%20sharing%20of%20these%20details%20is%20common%20practice%20among%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704277440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fh6gkofgg_mahua-moitra_625x300_02_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-gets-no-supreme-court-relief-asked-to-reply-to-notice-4792248%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20declined%20to%20look%20into%20the%20expulsion%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Mahua%20Moitra%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20in%20a%20setback%20to%20the%20leader%20who%20faces%20cash-for-query%20allegations%20linked%20to%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-gets-no-supreme-court-relief-asked-to-reply-to-notice-4792248%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-gets-no-supreme-court-relief-asked-to-reply-to-notice-4792248%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-gets-no-supr