3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20instance%20where%20the%20former%20actress%20has%20spoken%20out%20about%20the%20negative%20aspects%20of%20the%20Hindi%20film%20industry.%20Last%20year%2C%20she%20candidly%20discussed%20her%20experience%20with%20the%20casting%20couch%20in%20Bollywood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20experience%2C%20Suchitra%20Krishnamoorthi%20said%20that%20a%20filmmaker-producer%20once%20asked%20her%20to%20spend%20the%20night%20with%20him.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20meeting%20in%20a%20hotel%2C%20and%20in%20those%20days%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20meetings%20happened%20in%20hotels.%20It%20was%20quite%20common.%20I%20said%20that%20I%20am%20very%20close%20to%20my%20father.%20He%20said%2C%20'Very%20nice%2C%20then%20call%20your%20father%20and%20tell%20him%20that%20I%20will%20drop%20you%20back%20home%20tomorrow%20morning%2C'%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuchitra%20Krishnamoorthi%20added%20that%20it%20took%20a%20while%20for%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bprocess%26quot%3B%20what%20was%20happening.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20almost%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20tears.%20I%20picked%20up%20all%20my%20stuff%2C%20and%20I%20said%20I'm%20just%20coming%2C%20and%20I%20ran.%20It%20takes%20you%20a%20while%20to%20process.%20Then%20I%20was%20like%2C%20It's%204-5%20pm%20right%20now.%20What%20am%20I%20going%20to%20do%20with%20him%20until%20tomorrow%20morning%3F%20Then%20it%20started%20striking%20me%20what%20he%20was%20probably%20intending%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704276360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F9u95rr9o_-suchitra_625x300_13_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Forry-culture-is-dangerous-suchitra-krishnamoorthi-shares-what-her-friend-said-4792509%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Suchitra%20Krishnamoorthi%20expressed%20worries%20about%20the%20film%20industry's%20'Orry%20culture'%20emphasizing%20prominence%20over%20talent%2C%20linked%20to%20popularity.%22%2C%22au