bha%E2%80%99s%20actions%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-mahua-moitra-expulsion-lok-sabha-unethical-conduct-cash-for-query-allegations-245741%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20appeared%20to%20oppose%20this%20line%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20sovereign%20organ%20of%20the%20State%20is%20deciding%20its%20internal%20discipline.%20What%20is%20the%20scope%20of%20judicial%20review%2C%20if%20at%20all%3F%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20said%20that%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretary%20general%E2%80%99s%20reply%20is%20to%20be%20filed%20within%20three%20weeks.%20Moitra%20will%20get%20an%20additional%20three%20weeks%20to%20file%20a%20rejoinder%2C%20if%20any.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20who%20is%20counsel%20for%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20pleaded%20with%20the%20court%20that%20Moitra%20be%20allowed%20to%20attend%20Lok%20Sabha%20proceedings%20in%20the%20meantime%20as%20an%20interim%20measure.%20The%20court%20did%20not%20grant%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoitra%20is%20lawmaker%20from%20Krishnanagar%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20On%20December%208%2C%20she%20was%20expelled%20after%20an%20ethics%20committee%20report%20accused%20her%20of%20unethical%20conduct%20over%20a%20cash-for-query%20allegations%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chairperson%20of%20the%20committee%20is%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20MP%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Sonkar.%20Moitra%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fparliamentary-ethics-committee-opposition-mps-mahua-moitra%5C%22%3Eslammed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20probe%20as%20%E2%80%98filthy%2C%20unethical%2C%20misogynistic%E2%80%99.%20Several%20opposition%20MPs%20had%20walked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20came%20after%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20along%20with%20a%20lawyer%2C%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%20%E2%80%93%20termed%20by%20Moitra%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98jilted%20ex%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20had%20filed%20the%20complaint%20with%20the%20committee%20alleging%20that%20the%20TMC%20MP%20had%20accepted%20bribes%20from%20Dubai-based%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20to%20ask%20questions%20in%20parliament.%20The%20complaint%20said%20Moitra%20had%20shared%20the%20password%20of%20the%20official%20email%20of%20her%20Lok%20Sabha%20account%20with%20Hiranandani%2C%20claiming%20it%20had%20compromised%20%E2%80%98national%20security%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Singhvi%20in%20court%20cited%20what%20was%20standard%20practice%20for%20MPs%20%E2%80%93%20to%20delegate%20work%20to%20secretaries%20and%20assistants%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20uploading%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCan%20an%20MP%20not%20delegate%20her%20work%3F%20Imagine%20Hiranandani%20to%20be%20her%20secretary%20for%20a%20minute.%20Now%20you%20can%20say%20that%20he%20is%20not%20her%20secretary%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20asked%20him%20if%20he%20is%20accepting%20that%20a%20one-time%20password%20was%20shared%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704271518000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F07170726%2F2022_4img04_Apr_2022_PTI04_04_2022_000155B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-lok-sabha-secretariat-mahua-moitra%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20apex%20court%20said%20that%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretary%20general's%20reply%20is%20to%20be%20filed%20within%20three%20weeks.%20Moitra%20will%20get%20an%20additional%20three%20weeks%20to%20file%20a%20rejoinder%2C%20if%20any.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-lok-sabha-secretariat-mahua-moitra%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22REC%20Ltd%2C%20RVNL%20