0a%20reason%20or%20being%20told%20where%20his%20next%20posting%20will%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Railways%20is%20one%20of%2019%20zones%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndian%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Railways.%20An%20Amravati-based%20social%20activist%2C%20Ajay%20Bose%2C%20had%20filed%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%20queries%20with%20five%20of%20those%20zones%20%E2%80%93%20Central%20Railways%2C%20Western%2C%20Southern%2C%20Northern%2C%20and%20North%20Western%20Railways%20%E2%80%93%20asking%20for%20details%20on%20costs%20associated%20with%20the%20selfie%20booths.%20The%20Central%20Railways%20was%20the%20only%20zone%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20query%20on%20specific%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20response%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20in%20the%20Central%20Railway%20Zone%20alone%2C%20around%2020%20%E2%80%9Cpermanent%E2%80%9D%20selfie%20booths%20have%20been%20installed%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20Rs%206.25%20lakh%20each%2C%20totalling%20to%20Rs%201.25%20crore.%20There%20are%20another%2032%20odd%20%E2%80%9Ctemporary%E2%80%9D%20selfie%20booths%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20each%20(a%20total%20of%20Rs%2040%20lakh).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20information%20from%20CR%20was%20supplied%20by%20deputy%20GM%20Abhay%20Mishra%2C%20but%20the%20CPRO%20has%20been%20shunted%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bose%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManaspure%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20Swapnil%20D.%20Nila%2C%20who%20refused%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20change.%20Other%20officials%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctop-level%20decision%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERailway%20stations%20are%20just%20one%20of%20the%20many%20places%20where%20the%20government%20is%20using%20taxpayer%20money%20to%20put%20up%20these%20Modi%20selfie%20points.%20Universities%2C%20public%20areas%2C%20etc.%20too%20have%20seen%20these%20selfie%20points%20spring%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704266454000%2C%22visual