India's%20northern%20states.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67869918%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67869918.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67869918.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taiwan%20detects%20four%20Chinese%20balloons%20ahead%20of%20election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704256930000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106502484%2Cimgsize-7668.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftaiwan-detects-four-chinese-balloons-ahead-of-election%2Farticleshow%2F106502484.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106502484.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFour%20Chinese%20balloons%20were%20detected%20moving%20across%20the%20median%20line%20separating%20Taiwan%20from%20China%2C%20with%20three%20flying%20directly%20above%20the%20island%2C%20Taipei's%20defence%20ministry%20said%20Wednesday.%20Tuesday's%20balloon%20incidents%20came%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%20before%20the%20self-ruled%20island%20will%20hold%20a%20pivotal%20election%20and%20was%20the%20second%20consecutive%20day%20such%20objects%20were%20detected%20above%20Taiwan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftaiwan-detects-four-chinese-balloons-ahead-of-election%2Farticleshow%2F106502484.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftaiwan-detects-four-chinese-balloons-ahead-of-election%2Famp_articleshow%2F106502484.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftaiwan-detects-four-chinese-balloons-ahead-of-election%2Famp_articleshow%2F106502484.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rules%20Under%20CAA%20Now%20Ready%2C%20Likely%20to%20Be%20Notified%20Before%202024%20Elections%3A%20Reports%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F07121932%2FUntitled-design-2021-12-07T121919.360.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EReports%20say%20that%20the%20ruled%20under%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%20%E2%80%93%20under%20works%20ever%20since%20the%20Act%20was%20passed%20at%20the%20end%20of%202019%20%E2%80%93%20are%20now%20ready%20and%20will%20be%20notified%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20December%2010%2C%202019%20and%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20two%20days%20later%20after%20it%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20upper%20house%20by%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20The%20move%20drew%20heavy%20criticism%20from%20politicians%20and%20citizens%20alike%20for%20ostensibly%20singling%20out%20Muslims%20and%20excluding%20them%20from%20its%20purview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Act%20aims%20to%20provide%20citizenship%20to%20Hindus%2C%20Parsis%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Jains%20and%20Christians%20purportedly%20fleeing%20persecution%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20Muslim-majority%20neighbours%3B%20namely%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notable%20absence%20of%20Muslims%20from%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20legislation%2C%20irrespective%20of%20whether%20or%20not%20they%20are%20being%20persecuted%20in%20their%20countries%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20unconstitutional%20nature%20of%20the%20legislation%20when%20coupled%20with%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%2C%20had%20drawn%20widespread%20protests%20from%20thousands%20of%20citizens%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20protests%20and%20violence%20that%20ensued%2C%20the%20government%20notified%20the%20law%20in%20January%202020.%20Yet%2C%20the%20rules%20have%20remained%20unwritten%20until%20now%2C%20four%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fgovt-ready-with-rules-for-caa-set-to-be-notified-before-lok-sabha-polls-announcement-9092566%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20rules%20are%20now%20ready%20and%20an%20online%20portal%20to%20apply%20for%20citizenship%20under%20the%20CAA%20is%20also%20in%20place.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20going%20to%20issue%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20CAA%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20Once%20the%20rules%20are%20issued%2C%20the%20law%20can%20be%20implemented%20and%20those%20eligible%20can%20be%20granted%20Indian%20citizenship%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20quoted%20sources%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20things%20are%20in%20place%20and%20yes%2C%20they%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20implemented%20before%20the%20elections.%20The%20applicants%20will%20have%20to%20declare%20the%20year%20when%20they%20entered%20India%20without%20travel%20documents.%20No%20document%20will%20be%20sought%20from%20the%20applicants.%20Requests%20of%20the%20applicants%2C%20who%20had%20applied%20after%202014%2C%20will%20be%20converted%20as%20per%20the%20new%20rules%2C%E2%80%9D%20these%20sources%20continued%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20timing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fcitizenship-cut-off-date-likely-to-be-extended-beyond-dec-31-2014%2Farticleshow%2F106494250.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reports%20that%20the%20deadline%20put%20in%20place%20in%20the%20original%20Act%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20limited%20to%20those%20who%20had%20come%20to%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014%20%E2%80%93%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20extended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leaders%20have%20brought%20up%20the%20CAA%20multiples%20times%20in%20rallies%20and%20promised%20that%20the%20Act%20will%20soon%20be%20functioning.%20Most%20recently%2C%20Shah%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20West%20Bengal%20last%20week%2C%20%E2%80%9CDidi%20(West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee)%20often%20misleads%20our%20refugee%20brothers%20regarding%20the%20CAA.%20Let%20me%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20CAA%20is%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%20and%20no%20one%20can%20stop%20it.%20Everybody%20is%20going%20to%20get%20citizenship.%20This%20is%20our%20party%E2%80%99s%20commitment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bunch%20of%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20legal%20validity%20of%20the%20CAA%20are%20pending%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20In%20October%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-caa-hearing-mha-affidavit%5C%22%3Esubmitted%20an%20affidavit%20in%20the%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%20defending%20the%20law%20and%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbenign%20piece%20of%20legislation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704256899000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F07121932%2FUntitled-design-2021-12-07T121919.360.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frules-under-caa-now-ready-likely-to-be-notified-before-2024-elections-reports%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20became%20a%20law%20in%20December%202019%2C%20but%20has%20been%20non-functional%20for%20the%20last%20four%20years%20as%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20sought%20repeated%20extensions%20to%20frame%20the%20rules%20under%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frules-under-caa-now-ready-likely-to-be-notified-before-2024-elections-reports%22