A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdeaths-of-indian-origin-couple-daughter-in-massachusetts-ruled-murder-suicide%2Farticleshow%2F106501457.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106501457.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20deaths%20of%20a%20wealthy%20Indian-origin%20couple%20and%20their%20daughter%20in%20the%20US%20state%20of%20Massachusetts%20last%20week%20have%20been%20ruled%20a%20murder-suicide%20by%20medical%20authorities%20after%20autopsy.%20Rakesh%20Kamal%2C%2057%2C%20his%20wife%20Teena%20Kamal%2C%2054%20and%20their%20college-going%20daughter%20Arianna%20Kamal%2C%2018%20were%20found%20dead%20in%20their%20USD%205%20million%20mansion%20in%20Dover%2C%20Massachusetts%20on%20December%2028%2C%202023.%20A%20press%20release%20issued%20by%20the%20office%20of%20Norfolk%20District%20Attorney%20Michael%20Morrissey%20said%20that%20autopsy%20results%20issued%20by%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Chief%20Medical%20Examiner%20confirm%20that%20Teena%20and%20her%20daughter%20Arianna%20were%20victims%20of%20homicide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdeaths-of-indian-origin-couple-daughter-in-massachusetts-ruled-murder-suicide%2Farticleshow%2F106501457.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdeaths-of-indian-origin-couple-daughter-in-massachusetts-ruled-murder-suicide%2Famp_articleshow%2F106501457.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdeaths-of-indian-origin-couple-daughter-in-massachusetts-ruled-murder-suicide%2Famp_articleshow%2F106501457.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bharat%20Jodo%20Abhiyan%20Launches%20Month-Long%20Campaign%20to%20Celebrate%20India's%20Plural%20Cultural%20Heritage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Abhiyan%20(BJA)%20%E2%80%93%20a%20civil%20society%20platform%20involving%20organisations%20from%20across%2015%20states%20%E2%80%93%20on%20Tuesday%20(January%202)%20launched%20a%20month-long%20campaign%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Jana%20Gana%20Mana%20Abhiyaan%E2%80%99.%20This%20campaign%2C%20according%20to%20the%20organisers%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Can%20effort%20to%20revitalise%20citizens%20who%20take%20pride%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20rich%2C%20diverse%2C%20plural%20cultural%20heritage%20and%20work%20towards%20a%20society%20based%20on%20constitutional%20values%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20press%20conference%20to%20launch%20the%20Abhiyaan%20on%20Tuesday%20was%20addressed%20by%20Yogendra%20Yadav%20and%20Vijay%20Mahajan%20(convenors%20of%20BJA)%2C%20Kavitha%20Kuruganti%20(national%20secretary%2C%20BJA)%20and%20Kamayani%20Swami%20(national%20working%20group%20member%2C%20BJA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20country%20is%20witnessing%20a%20frenzy%20of%20organized%20communalism%20which%20has%20got%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20maryaada%20or%20Aastha%20or%20dharma%20but%20is%20a%20brazen%20attempt%20to%20polarize%20voters%20on%20religious%20lines%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20critical%202024%20national%20elections.%20At%20this%20fork-on-the-road%2C%20civil%20society%2C%20represented%20by%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Abhiyan%20(BJA)%20would%20like%20to%20remind%20Indian%20citizens%20and%20society%20of%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20strengths%20and%20assets%3A%20its%20immortal%20founders%2C%20incomparable%20heritage%2C%20diverse%20peoples%20and%20their%20varied%20cultures.%20We%20invite%20all%20like-minded%20citizens%20who%20take%20pride%20in%20our%20progressive%2C%20inclusive%20civilization%20and%20are%20committed%20to%20our%20constitutional%20values%20of%20fraternity%2C%20liberty%2C%20equality%20and%20justice%20to%20give%20us%20a%20missed%20call%20on%207877722353.%20We%20invite%20them%20to%20become%20co-travellers%20in%20this%20mission%20of%20unity%20and%20progress%2C%20for%20a%20healthy%20%E2%80%93%20inclusive%2C%20truth-seeking%2C%20forward-looking%2C%20and%20compassionate%20%E2%80%93%20society.%20We%20call%20upon%20them%20to%20join%20this%20vital%20mission%20to%20reclaim%20the%20republic%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20BJA%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agenda%20for%20the%20month%20includes%20both%20online%20and%20offline%20events%20starting%20from%20January%203.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20activities%20planned%20for%20the%20campaign%20include%20videos%2C%20posters%2C%20challenges%2C%20on-line%20and%20face-to-face%20local%20events%20which%20will%20help%20revive%20discussions%20around%20the%20ideals%20of%20the%20community%20we%20had%20imagined%20and%20re-kindle%20aspirations%20towards%20realising%20our%20cherished%20values%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20BJA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJA%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20comes%20in%20the%20same%20month%20as%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20on%20the%20land%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20once%20stood.%20Several%20opposition%20parties%20have%20said%20they%20will%20not%20be%20attending%20the%20January%2024%20event%20planned%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20as%20religion%20is%20a%20personal%20matter%20and%20should%20not%20be%20politicised.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704254370000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbharat-jodo-abhiyan-launches-month-long-campaign-to-celebrate-indias-plural-cultural-heritage%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Jana%20Gana%20Mana%20Abhiyaan%20is%20is%20%26quot%3Ban%20effort%20to%20revitalise%20citizens%20who%20take%20pride%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20rich%2C%20diverse%2C%20plural%20cultural%20heritage%20and%20w