nt-caption%5C%22%3ESaloni%20completed%20her%20MBBS%20from%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Lady%20Hardinge%20Medical%20College%20in%202012.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaloni%E2%80%99s%20quest%20for%20knowledge%20helped%20her%20crack%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321822%2Fraised-by-single-mom-ias-officer-donge-revaiah-shares-inspiring-upsc-journey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%20examination%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20her%20very%20first%20attempt.%20With%20a%20year%E2%80%99s%20preparation%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20achieve%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%2074.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Saloni%20was%20allocated%20to%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20cadre.%20Post%20her%20marriage%20with%20IAS%20Ashish%20Vashishta%2C%20she%20joined%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20cadre.%20For%20their%20marriage%2C%20Saloni%20paid%20a%20court%20fee%20of%20Rs%20500%20and%20reported%20to%20work%20within%20two%20days.%20She%20has%20been%20praised%20for%20her%20simplicity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202014-batch%20IAS%20officer%20shares%20her%20strategy%20for%20the%20first-time%20aspirants%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDo%20not%20follow%20what%20everyone%20else%20does%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20advises%20UPSC%20aspirants%20to%20not%20follow%20a%20blanket%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFigure%20out%20what%20works%20out%20best%20for%20you.%20You%20need%20to%20have%20a%20very%20customised%20approach%20for%20yourself.%20Some%20people%20prefer%20studying%20in%20groups%2C%20some%20prefer%20to%20study%20alone%20in%20a%20room.%20That%20is%20totally%20okay%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBe%20consistent%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20Saloni%20had%20roughly%20a%20year%20for%20preparation%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20be%20consistent%20in%20her%20preparation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPreparin