4-1700746994-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-4-1700746994-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-4-1700746994-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334808%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20says%20she%20did%20not%20give%20any%20fancy%20answers%20to%20the%20interviewers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaloni%20stressed%20that%20giving%20more%20mocks%20does%20not%20help%20if%20aspirants%20do%20not%20analyse%20them.%20%E2%80%9CUltimately%2C%20their%20purpose%20is%20to%20teach%20you%20from%20your%20mistakes.%20The%20whole%20exercise%20is%20futile%20if%20you%20do%20not%20analyse%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20craft%20a%20powerful%20essay%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUPSC%20examination%20tests%20not%20only%20the%20content%20of%20your%20essay%20but%20also%20your%20writing%20skills%2C%20the%20flow%20of%20ideas%2C%20and%20how%20aspirants%20weave%20it%20all%20together.%20Saloni%20says%20acing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F189965%2Fupsc-exam-ias-topper-tips-essay-paper-cse-mains-interview-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eessay%20writing%20%3C%2Fa%3Edoes%20not%20happen%20in%20a%20single%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20her%20strategy%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wondered%20what%20kind%20of%20writing%20engages%20me%20as%20a%20reader.%20I%20would%20read%20the%20editorial%20section%20of%20The%20Hindu%20and%20write%20down%20my%20inference%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20story.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20incorporated%20that%20same%20style%20in%20my%20answer%20writing.%20Your%20essay%20should%20be%20crisp%2C%20engaging%2C%20and%20backed%20by%20facts.%20You%20can%20also%20include%20flowcharts%20to%20make%20answers%20interesting%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENo%20fancy%20answers%20in%20the%20interview%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333542%2Fupsc-cse-interview-round-tips-by-ias-officers-personality-test-toppers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20IAS%20officer%20%3C%2Fa%3Esays%20she%20did%20not%20give%20any%20fancy%20answers%20to%20the%20interviewers.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20just%20myself%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%20an%20instance%20from%20her%20interview.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20state-level%20silver%20medalist%20in%20taekwondo.%20I%20remember%20I%20was%20told%20that%20I%20looked%20so%20fragile%20and%20that%20it%20did%20not%20look%20like%20I%20could%20practice%20taekwondo.%20I%20politely%20said%20that%20strength%20matters%20more%20than%20physical%20appearance.%20I%20was%20not%20like%20%E2%80%98Oh%2C%20my%20god%2C%20sir%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20about%20willpower%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20too%20senior%3B%20they%20understand%20when%20you%20are%20not%20being%20yourself.%20They%20do%20not%20appreciate%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Saloni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Mandla%20District%20Collectorate%20Facebook%2C%20Saloni%20Sidana%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700747920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334751%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Saloni%20Sidana%20pursued%20civil%20services%20after%20completing%20her%20MBBS.%20She%20aced%20UPSC%20CSE%2C%20securing%2074th%20rank%20in%20her%20first%20attempt.%20Serving%20as%20Mandla's%20district%20collector%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20s